query:
SELECT 
  l.name as league_name,
  COUNT(f.id) as matches_count
FROM fixtures f
JOIN leagues l ON f.leagueId = l.id
GROUP BY l.id, l.name
ORDER BY matches_count DESC
LIMIT 15;
